netpirate,

Tip: I wouldn't super-seed if I were you. It's a dumb way unless you're the only seeder; after that it's pretty hard to get rid of the setting in your bt client.

Will put a drawback on a torrent when you download, but will work fine when you are the lone seeder on a future one.

Myself I never super-seed, even if I'm the lone seeder... but, by all means, it's your own choice
